snippet.title: EVE Online | Havoc – Expansion Trailer
snippet.description:
Bring chaos to the frontlines with the upcoming Havoc expansion, as you align with either the Angel Cartel or Guristas pirate factions to aid the mysterious Deathless in spreading corruption throughout empire warzones from the newly discovered Zarzakh system! 

Havoc also introduces the new Vanguard FPS module into EVE Online, plus brand-new Angel Cartel and Guristas ships, updates to Corporation Projects, AIR Opportunities, and more.

#eveonline #mmo #spacegames #expansion 

Start playing EVE for free at http://EVE.Online/Fly_Now
